<mxCell id="legend" value="Color: blue=trigger (timer) · green=harness/artifacts (deterministic bash) · orange=gate·CI·publish · purple=models/self-evolution (AI) · yellow=human action.&#10;Key point: 🔑 the HMAC signing key lives only on the harness (VM) — models only produce text and never see the key, so a hijacked model can't forge or leak a signature. Adoption (merge) is a human gate." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f6f8fa;strokeColor=#d0d7de;fontColor=#1f2328;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="1000" width="1580" height="50" as="geometry"/></mxCell>

